{
  "stem": "3605.5",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 13.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I told the girls, we have to kind of crawl out on our stomach, and everybody should go the different directions.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "If we get caught, we shouldn't all get caught together.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Maybe some of us will survive.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I went into a farmer's house.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And her men were on the phone-- the son and the husband.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And she let me in, and she let me sleep over the night with the pigs.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I remember that I shared the potatoes with the pigs, and nothing ever tasted so good.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "She was so excited with the [NON-ENGLISH] coming, which is the enemy coming, that she didn't even give me anything else to eat.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "She just told me-- when I told her that I am a Polish worker-- I didn't tell her that I was Jewish-- that I am a Polish worker that was in a work camp.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So she told me that she has a Pole that is in a-- a prison-- American prison military camp-- POW.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And he is-- it is in that town.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was called the Vohl, that village that she was located.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And the man works for her during the day.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And sure enough, in the morning, that Polish fellow came, and we were talking with each other.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I didn't tell him that I am Jewish either.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "In the last camp, when we were sent from Bergen-Belsen, they gave us a regular coat with-- the back was cut out, and there were crosses.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But I sewed that back up, and I sewed the cross on.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So when I ran away, I took the cross off so I had like almost civilian clothes.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And we were talking with each other, with that young man.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And the American tanks walked in.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
